author: RTÉ News
title: WHO's Ryan calls for global solidarity to fight virus
description: The Executive Director of the WHO'S Health Emergencies Programme, Dr Mike Ryan, has called for global solidarity to fight the Covid-19 pandemic.
content:
The Executive Director of the WHO'S Health Emergencies Programme, Dr Mike Ryan, has called for global solidarity to fight the Covid-19 pandemic.
